<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      You've been invited to join the <%= @group.name %> learning group in Badge List. 
      To view the learning group, follow the link below to create a new Badge List account. 
      (Be sure to sign up using the same email address!)
    </p>
    <p>
      After you login you will see the learning group on your home page under "Your Groups".
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Create a Badge List account:</strong> 
      <a href="<%= "#{new_user_registration_path}?email=#{@to_email}&name=#{@to_name}" %>">
        <%= new_user_registration_path %>
      </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <i>
        This email was sent automatically by the Badge List app.
        Badge List is a badge-based tool for tracking learning progress. 
        If you take no action you will not receive any further emails about this invitation.
      </i>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>